		"description": "Complete API collection for Hospital Management System Backend.\n\nSetup:\n1. Import this collection\n2. Set environment variable `baseUrl` to `http://localhost:8080`\n3. Login first to get access token (auto-saved)\n4. All authenticated requests will use saved token",
